<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/new-genetic-biomarker-flags-aggressive-brain-tumors/">New genetic biomarker flags aggressive brain tumors</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
