		<title>Mayo Clinic scientists create tool to predict Alzheimer&amp;#8217;s risk years before symptoms begin</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-scientists-create-tool-to-predict-alzheimers-risk-years-before-symptoms-begin/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Alison Satake]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 12 Nov 2025 23:31:51 +0000</pubDate>
